---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="content">
		<section class="panel call-to-labor">
			<div class="dispatch-tag">[NEW DISPATCH]</div>
			<h2>THE 30-DAY STRUCTURAL AUDIT IS LIVE.</h2>
			<p class="lede">Stop guessing where the leak is. We have digitized the first 30 days of the project into a functional maintenance manual for your life.</p>
			<div class="cta-row">
				<a class="btn primary highlight" href="https://buy.stripe.com/dRmbIT2Z26pAbPPf7ZbV600" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GET THE AUDIT - $12.00</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="panel master-spec" id="book-manual">
			<h2>Materialist Christianity: Faith as a Living Foundation</h2>
			<p class="lede">The foundational text. If you need the complete schematic for why the old structures still hold weight, start here.</p>
			<div class="cta-row">
				<a class="btn primary" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FMN9T933" target="_blank" rel="noopener">READ THE MANUAL.</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="panel" id="field-notes">
			<h2>Field Notes (Free Archive)</h2>
			<p>Public dispatches on the friction of modern faith and the emptiness of modern atheism. Start here if the roof is leaking.</p>
			<article>
				<h3>Open circuits</h3>
				<ul class="clean-list">
					<li><a href="/start/atheist/">For the Atheist: The Empty Room</a></li>
					<li><a href="/start/christian/">For the Christian: The Corporate Church</a></li>
				</ul>
			</article>
		</section>

		<section class="panel vault-gate" id="structural-audits">
			<p class="section-label">Locked Dispatch</p>
			<h2>Structural Audits (The Vault)</h2>
			<p>Deep-dive teardowns of collapsing systems. $5/month to keep the lights on.</p>
			<div class="cta-row">
				<a class="btn primary" href="https://buy.stripe.com/dRmbIT2Z26pAbPPf7ZbV600" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SECURE THE AUDIT - $12.00</a>
			</div>
			<p>Broke? The labor is for the people. Email Ezra and I’ll send you the link. We're tradesmen, not landlords.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
